When: Tuesday 29-04-2025 12:30 - 17:00 Where: House of Connections, Grote Markt 21, Groningen
The PAGINA team invites you to an event where PhD student within the Graduate school of the Humanities present their project and work.
Are you interested in what we have done so far and what we will work on next? On April 29, we will present our project and first experiments, including preliminary results, in our talk called &ldquo;Reading Time Prediction for Dutch Text Simplification.&rdquo;
